               <p>I am apprentice to the prosecutor. The last witness and I followed him, and took him with the firkin upon him.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>A man asked me to carry it for him to Water-lane, Fleet-street; and he was to give me 6 d. for carrying it.</p>
